FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://polls.apiblueprint.org/

# golazo

Golazo is a simple API allowing consumers to view soccer seasons, games, teams and players.

## Seasons [/seasons]

### List All Seasons [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [{ "id":398,
           "seasonName":"Premier League 2015/16",
           "league":"PL",
           "year":"2015",
           "curMatchday":38,
           "numMatchdays":38,
           "numTeams":20,
           "numGames":380
         },
         { "id":399,
           "seasonName":"Primera Division 2015/16",
           "league":"PD",
           "year":"2015",
           "curMatchday":38,
           "numMatchdays":38,
           "numTeams":20,
           "numGames":380
         }]
          
## Filter Seasons [/seasons/{year}]
     
### List all seasons in a Year [GET]

+ Parameters
    + year (number) - year of the season in the form of an integer

+ Response 200 (application/json)

